{"tid":2083561,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"71行街人數靠你撩身邊人去，個個都是文宣！","createTime":"2020-06-28T23:34:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T08:40:58.000Z","uid":113155,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e3c39cc720e310474f61f9b4b3ff3ffc9cd79b06","tid":2083561,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T23:34:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">利申，已撩兩個</span></span>，本身冇諗住去，第三個冇fd陪唔去。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我只係問：「71去唔去。」</span></span><br />\nFd會係咁易講下唔知/難處，除咗不可抗力因素 eg考試，啲十九原因你可以遊說多兩句，真係黃嗰就會去，偽黃中立撚就算啦。"},{"pid":"3667ae96c6c07972a82ceb5c3335d3d1cadc620f","tid":2083561,"uid":113155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T23:36:33.000Z","msg":"我淨係撩五個，中兩個，其中一個會叫埋男友，即多三個；第三個考試，第四個做完嘢有冇時間去，第五個想但冇fd陪。<br />\n<br />\n命中率都幾高。"},{"pid":"e6a8a8b75a7e78a36ec843ed8b11523c6b097bcb","tid":2083561,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T23:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64daf19ea7119011ead09625803dd1444769dda3","tid":2083561,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T23:38:04.000Z","msg":"Ig fb文宣都要造勢！"},{"pid":"3c4d2534fbc2b294d1efb21f7a17e37aa03bb5a7","tid":2083561,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T23:39:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29264d748f642a8a1034e30404e823bc2170724d","tid":2083561,"uid":113155,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-28T23:43:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NFD1yhx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNFD1yhx.png&h=f7ba4f59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f5aa60068eb4b360